  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kuserfeedback</title>

    <para>
      The <application>kuserfeedback</application> package contains a
     	framework for collecting user feedback for applications via telemetry
      and surveys.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

